%F A008304 E.g.f. of column k: 1/Sum_{n>=0} ((k+1)*n+1-x)*x^((k+1)*n)/((k+1)*n+1)! - 1/Sum_{n>=0} (k*n+1-x)*x^(k*n)/(k*n+1)!. - _Alois P. Heinz_, Oct 13 2013
